title: Baytna Mediterranean Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegans will find choices such as falafel (gluten free also) hummus, baba ghanosh, fava bean salad, chopped tomato and cucumber salad and many more. All food is made-in-house to order. Offers unlimited add-ons to your falafel bowl (served on top of rice or salad greens). All sauces are vegan with the exception of the cucumber and mint yogurt dressing. Family owned business. Free Wi-Fi.
